# bunq Auto topdown

Auto Topdown is a Python script, to limit money in a bunq account to a specified amount, moving extra money
to another account.

## Installation

Install bunq Python SDK as speciefied https://www.bunq.com/de/developer

Locate the tinker folder and copy the auto_topdown.py script there.

## Usage

python auto_topdown.py  --topdown_from_account NL86BUNQ9900194780 --topdown_to_account NL86BUNQ9900194780 --amount 126.00

Will move any money more than 126.00 from the first account to the second.

